"title": "8791: oppression, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8791",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Oppression leads to the exploitation of the weak and vulnerable by the strong.</p>\n<h2>The victims</h2>\n<h3>The weak</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:5\">PSA 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2\">PSA 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:1\">ECC 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:4\">EZK 34:4</a></p>\n<h3>The poor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:22-Prov22:23\">PRO 22:22–22:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:6\">EXO 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:7\">DEU 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:7\">PRO 22:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:16\">PRO 22:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:27\">PRO 28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:29\">EZK 22:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6-Amos2:7\">AMO 2:6–2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:11-Amos5:12\">AMO 5:11–5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4\">AMO 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:6\">AMO 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:10\">ZEC 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:6\">JAS 2:6</a></p>\n<h3>Widows and orphans</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22\">EXO 22:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:17\">DEU 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:3\">JOB 24:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:9\">JOB 24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:21\">JOB 31:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:22\">JOB 31:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:5-Ps94:6\">PSA 94:5–94:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:10\">PRO 23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:23\">ISA 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:6\">JER 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:10\">ZEC 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:40\">MRK 12:40</a></p>\n<h3>The foreigner</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:21\">EXO 22:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:13\">GEN 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:9\">EXO 23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:33-Lev19:34\">LEV 19:33–19:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:7\">DEU 23:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:17\">DEU 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:6\">PSA 94:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:3\">JER 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:29\">EZK 22:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a></p>\n<h3>Servants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:14-Deut24:15\">DEU 24:14–24:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:6\">GEN 16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11\">EXO 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:9\">EXO 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13\">LEV 19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:3\">ISA 58:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:24\">ACT 7:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of oppression</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:6\">GEN 16:6</a> <em>Sarah oppresses Hagar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:39\">GEN 31:39</a> <em>Laban oppresses Jacob</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:8-Exod1:22\">EXO 1:8–1:22</a> <em>the Egyptians oppress Israel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:4\">ISA 52:4</a> <em>the Assyrians oppress Israel</em></p>\n<h2>The oppressors' motives</h2>\n<h3>Greed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:27-Jer5:28\">JER 5:27–5:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:5\">PRO 31:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:8-Eccl5:9\">ECC 5:8–5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:23\">ISA 1:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:2\">ISA 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:17\">JER 22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:1\">AMO 4:1</a></p>\n<h3>Lust for power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:10\">EXO 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:14\">2CH 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:10\">2CH 16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:15\">PRO 28:15</a></p>\n<h2>God's attitude to the oppressor</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22-Exod22:24\">EXO 22:22–22:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:19\">DEU 27:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:13\">PRO 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:5-Isa14:6\">ISA 14:5–14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:6\">JER 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:3-Jer22:5\">JER 22:3–22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3\">AMO 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:6\">AMO 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:9\">AMO 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:11\">AMO 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:1\">AMO 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:1\">ZEP 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:47\">LUK 20:47</a></p>\n<h2>The experience of oppression</h2>\n<h3>It brings grief and crying to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:9\">PSA 42:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:7\">EXO 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:18\">JDG 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:2\">PSA 43:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:1\">PSA 137:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:1\">ECC 4:1</a></p>\n<h3>The example of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7\">ISA 53:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:27-Matt27:31\">MAT 27:27–27:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:16-Mark15:20\">MRK 15:16–15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:32-Acts8:35\">ACT 8:32–8:35</a></p>\n<h3>Following Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22-Acts14:23\">ACT 14:22–14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:2-1Thess3:4\">1TH 3:2–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:3\">2TI 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:12</a></p>",
